  "remarks": "\nHead of the Southern District of the National Guard of the Russian Federation. Former de facto Commander of Russian troops deployed on the ground in the illegally annexed Crimea (whom Russia continues to refer to officially as ‘local self-defence militias’).  Former Deputy Commander of the Southern Military District.  Former Head of Department of Public Administration and National Security at the Military Academy of the Russian General Staff.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
